 🍗  Ingredients (For 1 serving)
▪ Chicken breast | 200 - 250 g 
 - (Chicken wings, thigh, tenderloin ... choose what you like !)
▪ Frying powder 
- (Tempura mix will be fine as well)
▪ Salt & Pepper

🍗 Soy Garlic Pepper Sauce 
▪ Soy sauce | 2T
▪ Oyster sauce | 1T
▪ Cooking wine | 2T
▪ Corn syrup | 5T
▪ Water | 2T
▪ Minced garlic | 0.5T
▪ Black Pepper
▪ Green & Red Peppers 

Deep frying at 170~180°C (350°F) and Double fry for extra crispness !
